# Distribution extensions — nevoflux-agent is now a built-in (system)
# extension bundled into omni.ja at builtin-addons/nevoflux-agent/ via
# src/nevoflux/engine-overlays/browser/extensions/nevoflux-agent/.
# distribution/extensions/ should stay empty; any *.xpi sitting here is
# a stale leftover from the old package-extension.sh path and (if
# shipped) gets auto-copied into the user profile on first launch,
# shadowing the built-in registration and triggering the
# "could not be verified" warning.
build/AppDir/distribution/extensions/

